"atiende eth0."

#: ../generic/server/C/network-config.xml:470(para) ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:941(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/network-config.xml:470(para)
msgid ""
"NOTE: dhcpd's messages are being sent to syslog. Look there for diagnostics "
